title: Opi Nail Lacquer, Not So Bora Pink, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: A rich, creamy pink with an exotic twist. Whenever you find yourself stuck in the office or in traffic staring down at your pink nails, this not so boring pink will have you longing for a tropical trip to Bora Bora.

title: Orly Nail Lacquer, Terracotta, 0.6 Fluid Ounce
description: Terracotta is a rich neon dark pink that is perfect for those spring and summer months while making your nails look just as amazing as the flowers out in your flower bed. Relax and enjoy your spring and summer days with this awesome pink color.

title: OPI Pirates of the Caribbean - Mermaid's Tears Nail Lacquer, 0.5 oz
description: From OPI, the Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides Collection includes trend-setting shades of pink, lavender and sage, and the new Silver Shatter - a stunning new shade that creates a "shattered" effect when applied over nail lacquer... It's "ARG-UABLY" the coolest thing you'll ever see!
